<!-- templates/weekly-report.hbs -->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>会员系统周报</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-top: none;
        }
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .stat-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            display: block;
        }
        .stat-label {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .chart-placeholder {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            height: 200px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #666;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-top: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>📊 会员系统周报</h1>
        <p>报告时间：{{reportDate}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>📈 核心指标</h2>
        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-number">{{totalActive}}</span>
                <span class="stat-label">活跃订阅</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-number">¥{{monthlyRevenue}}</span>
                <span class="stat-label">本月收入</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-number">{{expiringCount}}</span>
                <span class="stat-label">即将过期</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-number">{{autoRenewRate}}%</span>
                <span class="stat-label">自动续费率</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2>📊 套餐分布</h2>
        <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
            {{#each planDistribution}}
            <div style="margin: 10px 0; padding: 10px; background: white; border-radius: 5px;">
                <strong>{{@key}}:</strong> {{this}} 个订阅
                <div style="background: #007bff; height: 20px; width: {{this}}%; border-radius: 3px; margin-top: 5px;"></div>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>
        
        <h2>⚠️ 注意事项</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>本周有 {{expiringCount}} 个订阅即将过期，需要关注续费情况</li>
            <li>自动续费率为 {{autoRenewRate}}%，建议优化续费流程</li>
            <li>{{#if (gt totalExpired 0)}}有 {{totalExpired}} 个已过期订阅需要处理{{/if}}</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>💡 建议行动</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>对即将过期的用户发送个性化续费提醒</li>
            <li>分析高价值用户的使用模式，优化产品功能</li>
            <li>优化新用户引导流程，提高转化率</li>
            <li>考虑推出限时优惠活动提升续费率</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>此报告由系统自动生成</p>
        <p>如需更详细的数据分析，请登录管理后台查看</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
